{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot"]]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/swiftgodot\/cubemaparray"]}],"relationshipsSections":[{"title":"Inherits From","kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/ImageTextureLayered"],"type":"inheritsFrom"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/GodotObject","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/s23CustomStringConvertibleP","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/SQ","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/SH","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/s12IdentifiableP","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/VariantRepresentable","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/VariantStorable"],"title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo","kind":"relationships"}],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"CubemapArray"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"CubemapArray"}],"modules":[{"name":"SwiftGodot"}],"title":"CubemapArray","symbolKind":"class","roleHeading":"Class","externalID":"s:10SwiftGodot12CubemapArrayC","role":"symbol"},"sections":[],"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/CubemapArray\/createPlaceholder()"],"title":"Instance Methods"},{"title":"Type Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/CubemapArray\/godotClassName"]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An array of "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/Cubemap","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":"s, stored together and with a single reference.","type":"text"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/CubemapArray"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"CubemapArray","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"decla